{
  "texts": [
    "It was not something completely new to the literature world, but depending on its realization, the chatbot generated a concept that could be a start for further plot development.",
    "It is important not to blindly input the first generated chatbot's answers into work but to ask clarifying questions to make the story more comprehensive.",
    "However, character generation takes place in conjunction with the creation of the plot, so it is necessary to ask more about their temper, behavior, relationship, to get a complete image of a hero.",
    "In our case, the chatbot described in detail two loving couples, their characters, and the motives for their behavior and linked it to the main idea of the story.",
    "This information will be used for further descriptions, dialogues and stylistic device generation."
  ]
}